344
00:19:00,041 --> 00:19:01,375
[YASUMASA]
Yasuske!

345
00:19:18,166 --> 00:19:19,291
[RAIKOU]
Kosode.

346
00:19:23,625 --> 00:19:26,791
[howling]

347
00:19:26,875 --> 00:19:29,250
[screaming]

348
00:19:30,375 --> 00:19:31,583
