363
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:32,666
Hurry! Throw it at the Horror!

364
00:20:36,541 --> 00:20:39,708
[yelling]

365
00:20:47,250 --> 00:20:53,208
[screaming]

366
00:20:56,250 --> 00:20:58,041
