367
00:20:58,125 --> 00:21:01,583
No. I'm... I'm sorry, Yasusuke.

368
00:21:01,666 --> 00:21:02,791
I'm sorry.

369
00:21:05,791 --> 00:21:07,583
[SEIMEI]
Every single person.

370
00:21:07,666 --> 00:21:09,333
I told you. It's naïve
of you to think

371
00:21:09,416 --> 00:21:12,208
