396
00:22:11,875 --> 00:22:13,916
No.

397
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:16,750
I'll treasure it for
the rest of my life.

398
00:22:18,291 --> 00:22:19,333
My pants.

399
00:22:21,375 --> 00:22:23,541
I know.

400
00:22:23,625 --> 00:22:26,041
You may call me Hakamadare!

401
00:24:02,916 --> 00:24:05,416
[INARI A] While parents think
